title: BestOf

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the Sixers getting bounced from the playoffs. Should James Harden and Doc Rivers be brought back next year? Nick Wright calls Fritzy out for being oblivious to "First Things First" schedule. And Ross Tucker tells us who he thinks could be this year's Bengals.
